descriptionHtml:
Gatti 13 Ashes Armor for CBBEv3
--------------------------------------------------------------
I am not good at English. 
So enough support is not possible, please understand it.
Its my 14th equipment MOD.

The female Light/Heavy armor set.
include Armor,Gauntlets,Boots,Shoulders,Cloak.
Design inspration from \'BASTARD!! Online\'(Discontinued development) \'Ashes Nei\'.

*Craftable. \'Dragon\' Category. [b][color=red]Required \"Dragon Smithing\" perk.[/color][/b]

*if you have not smithing perk, use follow console command.
  help \"gatti 13\" 0  ...........; get IDs
  player.additem (ID) 1 .....; get items

* equipment slot information.
 Armor ..........:32_BODY
 Gauntlets .....:33_HANDS
 Boots ..........:37_FEET
 Cloak ...........:46
 Shoulder ......:45

Required ------------------------------------------------------
Caliente for Caliente\'s Body Mod - Big Bottom Edition v3

History -------------------------------------------------------
V1.1 Texture re-compressed at Texture-Optimizer.
....... Changed shoulder slot 50 to 45. (maybe there was problem at decapitated head)
V1.0 Release.

Credit --------------------------------------------------------
Thanks to

\'Caliente for Caliente\'s Body Mod - Big Bottom Edition v3\'
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666

Thanks for the video from [url=http://www.youtube.com/MrKrossFaith]MrKrossFaith[/url]
[youtube]-YzGybsqk2U[/youtube]
